### ğŸ”¨ Installation

#### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/mern-blog.git
cd mern-blog
cd server
npm install
**PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
